Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/rich-text/converting-jsx.mdx

Demonstrates the basic usage of the `RichText` component from `@payloadcms/richtext-lexical/react` to render `SerializedEditorState` data as JSX within a React component. This component includes built-in converters for common Lexical nodes.

